: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ota-onalarning farzandi kelajagiga mas&rsquo;uliyat bilan yondashuvi bolaning yaxshi kamol topishi va muvaffaqiyatga erishishidagi muhim omildir. Ota-onalar farzandining hayoti va ta&rsquo;lim-tarbiyasida faol ishtirok etsa, bolaning o&lsquo;sishi va rivojlanishi uchun maqbul muhitni ta&rsquo;minlay oladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Makroiqtisodiy va hududiy tadqiqotlar instituti ekspertlari O&lsquo;zbekistonda ota-onalarning farzand tarbiyasi va ta&rsquo;lim olishidagi ishtirokini aniqlash maqsadida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7-22 yosh</strong> oralig&lsquo;idagi farzandlari bor ota-onalar orasida so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazdi. So&lsquo;rovda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3602 nafar</strong> ota-ona ishtirok etdi (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">N=3602</strong>), ularning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">43 yosh</strong>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">75 foizi</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ni</strong> <em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ayollar</em>,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">25 foizi</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ni</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>esa&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">erkaklar</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;tashkil etdi.&nbsp;</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">U</em>larning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40 foizi</strong> oliy,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">37&nbsp;foizi</strong> o&lsquo;rta-maxsus va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">23 foizi</strong> o&lsquo;rta ma&rsquo;lumotga ega.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">26 foizini</strong> uy bekasi, ishsiz, nogiron va nafaqadagi shaxslar tashkil etdi. Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">66,7 foizi</strong> <em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">qiz&nbsp;</em>farzandning,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">33,3 foizi</strong> esa&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">o&lsquo;g&lsquo;il</em> farzandning ota-onasi. &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning fikriga ko&lsquo;ra, farzand tarbiyasiga onasi, otasi va aka-ukalari eng ko&lsquo;p ta&rsquo;sir o&lsquo;tkazadi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12,8 foizi o&lsquo;</strong>qituvchilarning ham ta&rsquo;siri borligini ta&rsquo;kidlagan.&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rovda qatnashganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">70 foizi</strong> farzandi buva-buvisi bilan istiqomat qilmasligini bildirgan. Aytib o&lsquo;tish joizki, bugungi kunda respublikadagi har bir oilaga&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">0,33 nafar</strong> qariya to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Farzandingiz kelajagini qanday tasavvur qilasiz, degan savolga respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">78,4 foiz</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">i</strong> ma&rsquo;lum bir kasbning mutaxassisi,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,8 foizi</strong> moddiy ta&rsquo;minlangan inson,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,4 foizi</strong> tadbirkor,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,3 foizi</strong> davlat xizmatchisi, deb javob bergan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,1 foizi</strong> biror narsaga erishishiga ko&lsquo;zim yetmaydi yoki tasavvur qila olmayman, deb javob bergan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rov natijasiga ko&lsquo;ra, ota-onalarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">94,6 foiz</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">i</strong> farzandi kelajagi haqida o&lsquo;zaro suhbatlashib turishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">86 foizi</strong> fikrlari bir-xil ekanligini ma&rsquo;lum qilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ota-onalarning&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">97,8 foiz</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">i</strong> farzandi bilan uning bo&lsquo;lajak kasbi va qiziqishlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida suhbatlashib turishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,2 foiz</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">i</strong> esa umuman bu haqida suhbatlashmaganini bildirgan. Ularning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">64,5 foizi</strong> <em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">qiz</em> farzandning ota-onasi, bo&lsquo;lib&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40 foizi</strong> oliy ma&rsquo;lumotga ega. &nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ota-onalarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">83,4 foizi</strong> farzandi tanlagan kasbni ma&rsquo;qullashini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,7 foizi</strong> umuman ma&rsquo;qullamasligini aytgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rov natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, yoshlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20,7 foizi</strong> shifokor,<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;18,2 foiz</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">i</strong> o&lsquo;qituvchi,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15,0 foizi</strong> jurnalist,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10,5 foiz</strong>i iqtisodchi,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7,8 foizi</strong> IT-sohasi,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,2 foizi</strong> tadbirkor,<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;5,3 foizi</strong> moliyachi<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;va 1 foizi</strong> huquqshunos bo&lsquo;lish istagida.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Qiz bolalar</em> asosan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">shifokor</strong> (24,3 foiz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&lsquo;qituvchi</strong> (22,5 foizi), jurnalist (21,1 foiz) va iqtisodchi (7 foizi) bo&lsquo;lishni rejalashtirmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">O&lsquo;g&lsquo;il bolalar</em> esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">iqtisodchi</strong> (17,5 foiz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">I<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">T-mutaxassisi</strong></strong> (14,3 foiz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">moliyachi</strong> (8,4 