td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); height: 26px; vertical-align: top; width: 205px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Iqtisodchi</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); height: 26px; vertical-align: top; width: 205px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Tadbirkor</h3></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); height: 28px; vertical-align: top; width: 204px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">IT-mutaxassisi</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); height: 28px; vertical-align: top; width: 205px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Moliyachi</h3></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); height: 28px; vertical-align: top; width: 205px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Sportchi</h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shu o&lsquo;rinda aytib o&lsquo;tish joizki, bugungi kunda nafaqat O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozori balki butun dunyoda aynan shifokor va o&lsquo;qituvchilarga talab juda yuqori, shuningdek, IT-sohasi mutaxassislariga ham talab baland, lekin shunga qaramay taklif ham juda yuqori. Biroq iqtisodchilarga talab yuqori emas. Mehnat bozorida marketolog, menejer va muhandislarga talab yuqori bo&lsquo;lishiga qaramay so&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etganlar orasida ushbu kasblarni tanlaganlar deyarli yo&lsquo;q. Bu esa o&lsquo;z navbatida yoshlar va ota-onalar orasida mehnat bozori tendensiyalari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlar yetarli darajada emasligidan dalolat beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">26,6 foizi</strong> farzandining kasb tanlashida ota-onasi turtki bo&lsquo;lganini bildirgan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">53,5 foizi</strong> bu to&lsquo;liq &nbsp;farzandining tanlovi ekanligini bildirgan va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">80 foiz</strong> ota-onalar farzandining qarorini qo&lsquo;llab-quvvatlashini aytgan.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,2 foiz</strong> respondentlar esa farzandi fikrini qo&lsquo;llab-quvvatlamasligini bildirgan. &nbsp; &nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">53,9 foizi</strong> farzandining ta&rsquo;lim olishi va uy ishlarini bajarishida talabchanlik qilishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">37,1 foizi</strong> esa shunchaki nazorat qilib turishini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,3 foizi</strong> esa talabchanlik ham, nazorat ham qilmasligini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rov natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, ota-onalarning bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">56,0 foizi</strong> farzandining ta&rsquo;lim olishdagi yutuqlaridan to&lsquo;liq qoniqishini bildirgan.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12,6</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foizi</strong> qoniqarli emas, deb baholagan. &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">75 foizi</strong> farzandi qo&lsquo;shimcha darslarga borishini bildirgan. Qo&lsquo;shimcha darslarga qatnamaydi, deb javob berganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">50 foizi</strong> o&lsquo;rtacha oylik daromadini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3 million</strong> so&lsquo;mgacha deb ko&lsquo;rsatgan, ya&rsquo;ni oilalarning moliyaviy xolati farzandining qo&lsquo;shimcha darslarga qatnashi bilan bog&lsquo;liq.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15,6 foiz</strong> respondentlar farzandining o&lsquo;qituvchisi bilan umuman muloqot qilmasligini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20,4 foizi</strong> haftada bir marotaba muloqot qilib turishini aytgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rov natijalaridan kelib chiqib, aytish mumkinki, bugungi kunda ota-onalar farzandining ta&rsquo;lim olishi va kelajakdagi hayoti haqida g&lsquo;amxo&lsquo;rlik qilmoqda. Lekin shunga qaramay ota-onalar orasida farzandi tarbiyasi va uning qiziqishlarini qo&lsquo;llab-quvvatlamaydiganlari ham kam emas. Shuningdek, bugungi kunda bolalarning qo&lsquo;shimcha darslarga qatnash ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari yuqori ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi, buning asosiy sababi esa maktablardagi ta&rsquo;lim sifatining pastligiga borib taqaladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Muhabbat Ahmedova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">MHTI loyiha rahbari</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ilhom Ikromov,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">MHTI yetakchi ilmiy xodimi</strong></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;">323</span></div></div></div></header></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></div>
